{"tid":140233,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(集思廣益) 有咩方法可以識多啲異性？","createTime":"2017-03-02T04:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T08:59:52.000Z","uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8114e703c814f723ea7c800e32d615a51db9cc0a","tid":140233,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:41:48.000Z","msg":"發覺出咗嚟做嘢，好多時都冇咩途徑識到異性。公司本身已經冇，又冇新人加入。身邊同年紀嘅女性朋友基本上都已經結婚/拍緊拖。而生活圈子又唔大，想搵人介紹都難。本身又冇咩異性朋友。咁仲可以點？有冇巴絲曾經面對差唔多情況，而後尾因為某啲方法而識到呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：冇拍拖，窮矮肥柒，冇車有樓。就30。"},{"pid":"e17b566ed606c51eab452a1fadeb84ed4e01b092","tid":140233,"uid":25070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:59:45.000Z","msg":"做邊行？"},{"pid":"2641c38affc3e34e072261410f95509044460379","tid":140233,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:15:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做邊行？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOffice咋，啱啱分手，一諗到再要去識異性就好不安 好驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8056fab40e0a0b546091654dbed1e07c8d3af5ca","tid":140233,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:42:31.000Z","msg":"你話自己有樓 就會有女"},{"pid":"940a4f77f7ba4e10bf97086cd7d6d26e79aeea69","tid":140233,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:23:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你話自己有樓 就會有女</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係都識唔到，點同佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db00f6e22e19e3f6bff61dbcff0e8e336a7f4e91","tid":140233,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:54:44.000Z","msg":"求意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53648209fdd01a90dfa3cfa294c79ac7f37d8b27","tid":140233,"uid":75452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:05:16.000Z","msg":"心口掛住個牌 寫住自己地址"},{"pid":"3d4cad610df778af006ec29d52f4c3e8913f643f","tid":140233,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T09:21:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>心口掛住個牌 寫住自己地址</blockquote><br />\n認真係㗎巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c0535393345e3f8b6a0cf71810755c81f546f4","tid":140233,"uid":25070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做邊行？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOffice咋，啱啱分手，一諗到再要去識異性就好不安 好驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfrd撘frd識人最簡單喇"},{"pid":"1c539b388d580ab9ec789ea85e577d3a2284a181","tid":140233,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:53:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做邊行？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOffice咋，啱啱分手，一諗到再要去識異性就好不安 好驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfrd撘frd識人最簡單喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來依個方法都好難， 周圍問人都話冇咩單身女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab251261d9a4a65737f3e6ac8f6eb4d87c44c073","tid":140233,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T00:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd414aaae02226811a298f7dbdfadbaee103205","tid":140233,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T00:23:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee536033aaf866b80b3bd021ad5d19be177b1d4b","tid":140233,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:47:40.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打有實例呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1a9991944db720ef941b385b23edd855956c5c","tid":140233,"uid":65656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:50:48.000Z","msg":"唔洗急啦岩岩散"},{"pid":"d9b0b49e7a6213842241a27638d4c6dc1d4c6cb7","tid":140233,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:59:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗急啦岩岩散</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明白現階段係唔應該搵住，但分吓心先，再慢慢陪養感情啫。我唔係好急，但想只有咩途徑囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}